## Edge Case Reference

| Field Kind | Handling |
|---|---|
| `'scalar'` | Included in all interfaces, mapped via `prismaTypeToTs` |
| `'enum'` | Included in all interfaces, type is the enum name; enum is generated in `enums.ts` |
| `'object'` (relations) | Excluded from all interfaces — not serializable as flat JSON |
| `'unsupported'` | Excluded (filter only includes `kind === 'scalar' \|\| kind === 'enum'`) |
| `isId: true` | Included in `WhereUniqueInput`; excluded from `CreateInput` and `UpdateInput` |
| `isUnique: true` | Included in `WhereUniqueInput` |
| `isRequired: false` | Gets `?` in base interface |
| `hasDefaultValue: true` | Gets `?` in `CreateInput` |
| `isReadOnly: true` | Excluded from `CreateInput` and `UpdateInput` |
| `isList: true` | Type becomes `T[]` |
| `isUpdatedAt: true` | Caught by `isReadOnly: true` (Prisma sets `@updatedAt` fields as read-only in DMMF) |
| `dmmf.datamodel.enums.length === 0` | `enums.ts` not generated, no import in `index.ts` |
| `dmmf.datamodel.models.length === 0` | Both `client.ts` and `index.ts` emit trivially; no models property on `RestClient` |

