## Context

Add a new Prisma generator package to the monorepo that implements the standard Prisma generator protocol (JSON-RPC over stdin/stderr) and, for each model in the schema, emits TypeScript interfaces and a typed `RestClient` class with CRUD methods (`findMany`, `findUnique`, `create`, `update`, `delete`). The package follows the exact same conventions used by `packages/adapter-pg` (the simplest bundled package in the repo) and hooks into the existing build and CI infrastructure.

